rows.label: qst701306_msg0001
rows.name:
We've been friends for many years, so
I know how brash that guy can get.

rows.label: qst701306_msg0002
rows.name:
Especially with chicks. He gets so
up himself, you could cut his head off
and he still wouldn't die.

rows.label: qst701306_msg0003
rows.name:
But this time, it feels different.
I can't help worrying...

rows.label: qst701306_msg0102
rows.name:
Whatever it is, I can tell it's not good.
What's the idiot done this time...?

rows.label: qst701306_msg0103
rows.name:
Has he run across an angry ex?
Gotten it on with a married woman?
Fallen for a honey trap scheme?

rows.label: qst701306_msg0104
rows.name:
I wouldn't put anything past him...
But whatever it is, I can handle it.
I mean, it's not like he's dead, right?
